on the contract to supply the royal navy with the rum for its daily rum tot a tradition under which all sailors were allocated a daily rum ration this tradition continued until  with man group holding the contract throughout the company further expanded from sugar and rum into other commodities such as coffee and cocoa the company traded as a commodities business throughout the th and th century gradually diversifying into financial services following the advent of financial exchanges to hedge commodity exposures the firm was renamed ed  f man in  based on the initials of james mans grandsons edward desborough man and fredrick man ed  f man listed on the london stock exchange in  in  the company divided into two entirely separate businesses with man group plc focusing exclusively on financial services and ed  f man the commodities division taken private in a management buyout in  man group moved into its present form as an investment management business following the demerger and flotation of its brokerage business known as mf global on the new york stock exchange man group attained its current structure over time through acquisition man ahl is the oldest investment manager of the group having been acquired over time from  to  man group’s other investment managers were acquired between  and  in  man group acquired man glg previously glg partners for  billion then man frm in  and man numeric in  structure and operationsedit man group head office at swan lane in london building in the background man group offers strategies across a variety of investment approaches styles and asset classes man ahledit founded in  man ahl is a diversified quantitative investment manager offering absolute return and longonly funds with both momentum and nonmomentum strategies in recent years the manager’s sales have shifted from retail to institutional investors man ahl has over  investment professionals man frmedit established in  and acquired by man group in  man frms  research and investment professionals operate from london new york tokyo guernsey and pfäffikonsz switzerland man glgedit man glg was established in london in  as glg partners it was publicly listed in  before being acquired by man group in  for  billion man glg is a multiteam discretionary investment manager man glg utilises absolute return and longonly strategies across asset classes sectors and geographies the january  acquisition of silvermine was expected to boost the division’s us clo business man numericedit man numeric was established in  and acquired by man group in  a bostonbased quantitative asset manager with  billion fum as at december  man numeric offers longonly active extension and hedged equity strategies man group acquired man numeric to build a diversified quantitative fund management business in nonmomentum strategies and to develop man group’s presence in the north american market in  man numeric’s average client portfolio outperformed industry benchmarks by  before fees strategyedit luke ellis was appointed as man group’s ceo in september  he succeeded manny roman whom ellis had worked with for seven years at man group and had known for two decades ellis strategic objective for man group is to continue diversifying the firm through acquisition as well as invest in its infrastructure man group has seen significant costcutting led by copresident jonathan sorrell with a  million costsaving programme planned for delivery in  achieved ahead of schedule sorrells role as president was expanded by ellis to include corporate strategy private markets and acquisitions mergers and acquisitionsedit table of man group mergers and acquisitions date ahl  glenwood capital investment llc glenwood global management llc and remaining  stake in man glenwood gmbhgroup nov  ord minnett strategic investments dec  rmf investment group may  bluecrest capital management ltd minority stake sold in   dec  pemba credit advisers an asset manager specialising in european credit portfolios ap