’s infrastructural capacity can provide the platform to give our clients access to these areas learn more about man gpm diversified offering institutional framework view man gpm strategies  as at  march  news  perspectives  environmental social and corporate governanceat man group we believe that responsible investing is fundamental to fulfilling our fiduciary duty learn more about what we are doing in the area of responsible and esg investing frm early view june june was a mixed month for hedge fund returns with equity longshort and relative value strategies generally performing well on increased single security alpha while credit and global macro struggled man booker prizesa horse walks into a bar by david grossman is announced as the winner of the  man booker international prize the novel was translated by jessica cohen and is published in britain by jonathan cape man gpm aaltoman gpm aalto ‘aalto’ forms the real assets business of man gpm aalto is a real asset investment manager offering differentiated debt and equity strategies in commercial and residential real estate join the man group teamwe pride ourselves on the quality of our people joining man group means becoming part of a high calibre team perspectivesat man group we believe that different investment styles and approaches can be effective and beneficial to each other as we challenge consensus and convention ahl explainsnarrated by man ahls chief scientist dr anthony ledford the ‘ahl explains’ video series explores key concepts in futures trend following programmes – bringing each concept to life by focusing on principles not details please update your browser unfortunately we no longer support internet explorer   and older for security reasons please update your browser to a later version and try to access our site again many thanks man group  wikipedia man group from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search man group plc type public traded as lse emg industry financial services founded   years ago  founder james man headquarters riverbank house  swan lane london united kingdom area served worldwide key people lord livingston chairman luke ellis group ceo jonathan sorrell president pierre lagrange senior advisor mark jones cfo designate sandy rattray chief investment officer robyn grew chief administrative officer products investment products revenue us million  operating income us million  net income us million  number of employees   divisions man ahl man glg man numeric investors man frm website mancom man group plc is an alternative investment management business initially founded as a sugar cooperage and brokerage by james man in  it provides a range of funds for institutional and private investors globally and is the worlds largest publicly traded hedge fund company reporting  billion in funds under management as of march  the firm is headquartered at riverbank house in london and employs over  people in various locations worldwide the company is a noted sponsor of the arts and charitable initiatives including the man booker prize and the man charitable trust in recent years the firm has made several acquisitions as part of its strategy to diversify the business particularly in the united states these acquisitions including man numeric a quantitative equity manager the firm has also seen a shift towards institutional clients and with its  acquisition of aalto and launch of man global private markets man gpm a move into private markets contents  history  structure and operations  man ahl  man frm  man glg  man numeric  strategy  mergers and acquisitions  rmf and bernard madoff  man booker prizes  corporate responsibility  man charitable trust  oxfordman institute  former sponsorships and charitable initiatives  see also  references  further reading  external links historyedit the company was founded by james man in  as a sugar cooperage and brokerage based in harp lane in billingsgate the following year man group won the contract to supply the royal navy with the rum for its daily rum tot a tradition under which all sailors were allocated a daily rum ration this tradition continued until  with man group holding the contract throughout the company further expanded from sugar and rum into other commodities such as coffee and cocoa the company traded as a commodities business throughout the th and th century gradually diversifying into financial services following the advent of financial exchanges to hedge commodity exposures the firm was renamed ed  f man in  based on the initials of james mans grandsons edward desborough man and fredrick man ed  f man listed on the london stock exchange in  in  the company divided into two entirely separate businesses with man group plc focusing exclusively on financial services and ed  f man the commodities division taken private in a management buyout in  man group moved into its present form as an investment management business following the demerger and flotation of its brokerage business known as mf global on the new york stock exchange man group attained its current structure over time through acquisition man ahl is the oldest investment manager of the group having been acquired over time from  to  man group’s other investment managers were acquired between  and  in  man group acquired man glg previously glg partners for  billion then man frm in  and man numeric in  structure and operationsedit man group head office at swan lane in london building in the background man group offers strategies across a variety of investment approaches styles and asset classes man ahledit founded in  man ahl is a diversified quantitative investment manager offering absolute return and longonly funds with both momentum and nonmomentum strategies in recent years the manager’s sales have shifted from retail to institutional investors man ahl has over  investment professionals man frmedit established in  and acquired by man group in  man frms  research and investment professionals operate from london new york tokyo guernsey and pfäffikonsz switzerland man glgedit man glg was established in london in  as glg partners it was publicly listed in  before being acquired by man group in  for  billion man glg is a multiteam discretionary investment manager man glg utilises absolute return and longonly strategies across asset classes sectors and geographies the january  acquisition of silvermine was expected to boost the division’s us clo business man numericedit man numeric was established in  and acquired by man group in  a bostonbased quantitative asset manager with  billion fum as at december  man numeric offers longonly active extension and hedged equity strategies man group acquired man numeric to build a diversified quantitative fund management business in nonmomentum strategies and to develop man group’s presence in the north american market in  man numeric’s average client portfolio outperformed industry benchmarks by  before fees strategyedit luke ellis was appointed as man group’s ceo in september  he succeeded manny roman whom ellis had worked with for seven years at man group and had known for two decades ellis strategic objective for man group is to continue diversifying the firm through acquisition as well as invest in its infrastructure man group has seen significant costcutting led by copresident jonathan sorrell with a  million costsaving programme planned for delivery in  achieved ahead of schedule sorrells role as president was expanded by ellis to include corporate strategy private markets and acquisitions mergers and acquisitionsedit table of man group mergers and acquisitions date ahl  glenwood capital investment llc glenwood global management llc and remaining  stake in man glenwood gmbhgroup nov  ord minnett strategic investments dec  rmf investment group may  bluecrest capital management ltd minority stake sold in   dec  pemba credit advisers an asset manager specialising in european credit portfolios april   interest in ore hill partners llc a provider of investment management services concurrently ore hill agreed to acquire a  stake in pemba credit advisers ltd from man group mar  man eco specialising in financing environmentally related projects man environmental capital opportunities april  nephila capital ltd june  glg partners may  frm holdings july  pine grove asset management aug  numeric holdings sept  fundoffunds assets from merrill lynch alternative investments may  silvermine capital management jan  newsmith llp’s investment management operations  may  aalto  october  rmf and bernard madoffedit rmf a former division of man group invested  of its funds under management at the time with various rd party funds which in turn had positions in funds ultimately managed by bernard madoff rmf was one of  financial institutions and  individuals to invest in such funds as of   of all such funds have been recovered and returned to various institutions and individuals man booker prizesedit man group has sponsored the man booker literary prize since  described by the telegraph newspaper as “arguably the uk’s most prestigious literary prize the £ award was created in  to increase the reading of quality fiction and attract “the intelligent general audience” each year the winner is announced at an awards dinner broadcast live by bbc television inclusion into the awards shortlist and attendant press coverage is known to provide a significant boost to book sales and bookstore visits with sales trebling in some cases the  prize was awarded to the new york novelist paul beatty for the sellout previous winners include philip roth and lydia davis the  award went to author richard flanagan for the narrow road to the deep north with his prize presented by chair of judges ac grayling at london’s guildhall it was the first year in which eligibility for the award was expanded to include any novel written in english and published in the uk man also sponsors the man booker international prize this £ prize is awarded each year on the basis of a single book translated into english and aims to encourage the publishing and reading of quality fiction in translation the prize is divided equally between author and publisher corporate responsibilityedit man group supports various charitable initiatives principally through the man charitable trust and the oxfordman institute man charitable trustedit set up in  the man charitable trust is an independent registered charity that funds small to mediumsize charities focusing on literacy and numeracy programmes it also funds programmes in support of access to education for disadvantaged people in  the trust awarded £ to uk charities including £ to beanstalk a charity that recruits and trains volunteers to provide reading support in primary schools and £ to national numeracy a charity dedicated to raising low levels of numeracy among adults and children oxfordman instituteedit in june  man launched a joint project with the university of oxford the oxfordman institute of quantitative finance man group’s initial financial commitment to the institute was £ million one of the largest single donations to a british higher education institution in recent years in  the oxfordman institute expanded its focus on machine learning and data analytics becoming part of the university of oxfords department of engineering science the development of the omis focus creates a hub for machine learning and data analysis at eagle house the current home of the omi and man ahls oxford research lab former sponsorships and charitable initiativesedit man group is a former sponsor of the man group international climate change award and the man asian literary prize in the s man was a founding member of the east london partnership which became the east london business alliance a businesscommunity outreach charity promoting corporate social responsibility and employee volunteering see alsoedit companies portal hedge fund man booker prize man booker international prize